title: LF (Plat 5+) Player (Any Role) for Dia Push
body:
As title states, looking for a fellow Plat 5 or above player wanting to push to Diamond in Dynamic Que.

Must be good at the role they choose. 

If you think you are good enough to push into Dia from Plat 5 (or above) add me...

IGN: nageV
